<p>John and Dave are local in New Hampshire, no bandwidth issues to get in the way today!  Just a straight-ahead podcast answering your questions, helping you change permissions, re-enable Airport, suss out GigE versus FireWire speeds, and even a follow-up on encrypting your data.  Good stuff!  Subscribe for free today.</p>
